# Trained model artifacts ARE tracked: they're small (~5MB total) and the
# Cloud Run build bakes them into the image. For production scale, switch
# to Cloud Storage and pull at startup — see docs/deployment_gcp.md.

# context/dataset/ duplicates data/raw/ — keep one tracked copy
context/dataset/
